&lt;/h1&gt;
&lt;p&gt;HTML give the structure to any website, it is like bone strucutre of the body. But the CSS makes it colorful, give some life imitation ability and make it beautiful, it is like flesh and skin on the bone which makes body alive and beautiful. This tutorial should give you a solid foundation in advanced CSS techniques. Keep practicing, with AI driven coding tools you need not memorize the syntext but you should understand what is possible so that you can imagine how you can use it for you project.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
      
